{"tid":2303641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網美把無辜入鏡情侶PO網惹公審 「我不道歉」稱雙方都有錯嗆告酸民","createTime":"2020-11-28T06:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T06:19:01.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e60746d07b76e6dbc898046080b5f2b6520bf851","tid":2303641,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"一對情侶日前到桃園JETS遊樂園，在摩天輪附近意外成為一名網美美拍的「背景」，影片中情侶出現不到5秒，卻被網美發到IG限時動態且寫「沒看到老娘在拍照？」情侶的朋友見狀轉發還TAG他們「是沒看到她娘在拍照喔」，網美更將2人的帳號公開再PO動態，情侶要求撤照又遭嗆，不少網友聲援他們，該名網美IG一度設為「私人帳號」，約中午又開放帳號，在限時動態影片中聲稱「我不道歉」，發文說未收到該對情侶的私訊，還截圖揚言要告酸民，「今天會報案做筆錄」<br />\n<br />\n新聞<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201126/ZDQOFERWQVGJVO5BUQ2ZQA3VYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201126%2FZDQOFERWQVGJVO5BUQ2ZQA3VYA%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Cma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=bdc39644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201126%2FZDQOFERWQVGJVO5BUQ2ZQA3VYA%2F&h=980bccb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201126/ZDQOFERWQVGJVO5BUQ2ZQA3VYA/</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/mood/p/234863223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Fmood%2Fp%2F234863223&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Cma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=a5f6a31b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/mood/p/234863223</a><br />\n<br />\n睇仆街仆街最開心"}]}